### [POST] Izveido kursa un programmas rezultātu sasaisti
POST http://localhost:8080/api/course-to-programme-results
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseInfo": { "id": "ced16f65-dfc7-4d5f-b599-300dab33e6bf" },
  "courseResult": { "id": "5c0425e1-f1a1-4a77-982a-a4ec2ae8c96e" },
  "programmeResult": { "id": "0de335dd-7e74-4512-b670-9cc4ddfa8815" }
}

###

### [GET] Iegūst visas sasaistes
GET http://localhost:8080/api/course-to-programme-results

###

### [GET] Iegūst konkrētu sasaisti pēc ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/course-to-programme-results/1

###

### [PUT] Atjaunina sasaisti ar ID = 1
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/course-to-programme-results/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseInfo": { "id": "ced16f65-dfc7-4d5f-b599-300dab33e6bf" },
  "courseResult": { "id": "5c0425e1-f1a1-4a77-982a-a4ec2ae8c96e" },
  "programmeResult": { "id": "36c56c5f-f8d1-4bdb-ba90-e6bdc3cfeae1" }
}

###

### [DELETE] Dzēš sasaisti ar ID = 1
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/course-to-programme-results/1
